Note:
Instant primitive KAT (Known Answer Test).

Coverage:
- instant_now returns a non-negative value (CLOCK_MONOTONIC).
- Successive instant_now readings are monotonically non-decreasing.
- instant_elapsed correctly computes the signed delta.
- instant_add_duration / subtract round-trip.
- instant_compare returns -1, 0, +1 with the expected semantics.
- instant_min / instant_max select the correct operand.
- instant_to_nanoseconds / instant_from_nanoseconds are inverses.

Exit code legend:
  0  All assertions passed.
  10 instant_now returned a negative sentinel.
  11 Monotonic ordering violated.
  12 instant_elapsed(start, end) returned wrong sign or magnitude.
  13 instant_add_duration / subtract round-trip failed.
  14 instant_compare returned wrong sign.
  15 instant_min / instant_max picked the wrong operand.
  16 instant_to_nanoseconds / instant_from_nanoseconds round-trip failed.
  17 instant_is_before / instant_is_after returned wrong value.
:End Note

Import "compiler/frontend/primitives/time/instant.runa" as Instant

Process called "main" returns Integer:
    Note: ----- Case 10: instant_now returns a non-negative reading -----
    Let t0 be proc instant_now from Instant
    If t0 is less than 0:
        Return 10
    End If

    Note: ----- Case 11: Monotonic ordering across consecutive reads -----
    Let t1 be proc instant_now from Instant
    Let t2 be proc instant_now from Instant
    If t1 is less than t0:
        Return 11
    End If
    If t2 is less than t1:
        Return 11
    End If

    Note: ----- Case 12: instant_elapsed -----
    Let delta_basic be proc instant_elapsed from Instant with 100, 250
    If delta_basic is not equal to 150:
        Return 12
    End If
    Let delta_reverse be proc instant_elapsed from Instant with 250, 100
    If delta_reverse is not equal to -150:
        Return 12
    End If
    Let delta_zero be proc instant_elapsed from Instant with 500, 500
    If delta_zero is not equal to 0:
        Return 12
    End If

    Note: ----- Case 13: instant_add_duration round-trip -----
    Let base be 1000000000
    Let after_add be proc instant_add_duration from Instant with base, 500
    If after_add is not equal to 1000000500:
        Return 13
    End If
    Let after_sub be proc instant_add_duration from Instant with after_add, -500
    If after_sub is not equal to base:
        Return 13
    End If

    Note: ----- Case 14: instant_compare -----
    Let cmp_lt be proc instant_compare from Instant with 100, 200
    If cmp_lt is not equal to -1:
        Return 14
    End If
    Let cmp_eq be proc instant_compare from Instant with 200, 200
    If cmp_eq is not equal to 0:
        Return 14
    End If
    Let cmp_gt be proc instant_compare from Instant with 300, 200
    If cmp_gt is not equal to 1:
        Return 14
    End If

    Note: ----- Case 15: instant_min / instant_max -----
    Let mn be proc instant_min from Instant with 100, 200
    If mn is not equal to 100:
        Return 15
    End If
    Let mx be proc instant_max from Instant with 100, 200
    If mx is not equal to 200:
        Return 15
    End If

    Note: ----- Case 16: instant_to_nanoseconds / from_nanoseconds round-trip -----
    Let ns_value be 999999999999
    Let i_val be proc instant_from_nanoseconds from Instant with ns_value
    Let ns_back be proc instant_to_nanoseconds from Instant with i_val
    If ns_back is not equal to ns_value:
        Return 16
    End If

    Note: ----- Case 17: instant_is_before / instant_is_after -----
    Let before_true be proc instant_is_before from Instant with 100, 200
    If before_true is not equal to 1:
        Return 17
    End If
    Let before_false be proc instant_is_before from Instant with 200, 100
    If before_false is not equal to 0:
        Return 17
    End If
    Let after_true be proc instant_is_after from Instant with 200, 100
    If after_true is not equal to 1:
        Return 17
    End If
    Let after_eq_false be proc instant_is_after from Instant with 200, 200
    If after_eq_false is not equal to 0:
        Return 17
    End If

    Return 0
End Process
